### =============================================================================
### GET /me — Home screen (login + pull-to-refresh)
### =============================================================================

### [1] Fresh fetch — cache miss → 5 parallel DB queries
###     Device should cache this for 30 days
GET {{baseUrl}}/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [2] Second hit — Redis cache hit → zero DB queries
GET {{baseUrl}}/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### =============================================================================
### GET /me/scans — Scan history screen
### =============================================================================

### [3] First page — all scans
GET {{baseUrl}}/me/scans?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [4] Emergency scans only
GET {{baseUrl}}/me/scans?filter=emergency&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [5] Cursor pagination — paste nextCursor from [3] response
GET {{baseUrl}}/me/scans?cursor=PASTE_NEXT_CURSOR_HERE&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### [6] Flagged (non-success) scans
GET {{baseUrl}}/me/scans?filter=flagged&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### =============================================================================
### PATCH /me/profile — Updates wizard (4-step, single batched call)
### =============================================================================

### [7] Full profile update (all 3 sections + contacts)
###     Response: { cache_invalidated: true } → device clears 30-day cache
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/me/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "student_id": "{{studentId}}",
  "student": {
    "first_name": "Aarav",
    "last_name": "Sharma",
    "class": "Class 9",
    "section": "A"
  },
  "emergency": {
    "blood_group": "B_POS",
    "allergies": "Penicillin, Peanuts",
    "conditions": "Mild asthma",
    "medications": "Salbutamol inhaler",
    "doctor_name": "Dr. Rajesh Mehta",
    "doctor_phone": "+919876543210",
    "notes": "Carry inhaler at all times"
  },
  "contacts": [
    { "name": "Suresh Sharma", "phone": "+919876543210", "relationship": "Father", "priority": 1 },
    { "name": "Meena Sharma",  "phone": "+919876543211", "relationship": "Mother", "priority": 2 }
  ]
}

###

### [8] Partial update — emergency only, no student/contacts
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/me/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "student_id": "{{studentId}}",
  "emergency": {
    "blood_group": "O_POS"
  }
}

###

### [9] Wrong phone format — expect 400 VALIDATION_ERROR
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/me/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "student_id": "{{studentId}}",
  "contacts": [
    { "name": "Test", "phone": "9876543210", "relationship": "Father", "priority": 1 }
  ]
}

###

### =============================================================================
### PATCH /me/visibility — Emergency + Visibility screens
### =============================================================================

### [10] Set visibility to PUBLIC, no hidden fields
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/me/visibility
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "student_id": "{{studentId}}",
  "visibility": "PUBLIC",
  "hidden_fields": []
}

###

### [11] Set to MINIMAL
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/me/visibility
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "student_id": "{{studentId}}",
  "visibility": "MINIMAL",
  "hidden_fields": []
}

###

### [12] PUBLIC but hide specific fields
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/me/visibility
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "student_id": "{{studentId}}",
  "visibility": "PUBLIC",
  "hidden_fields": ["medications", "notes"]
}

###

### [13] Invalid visibility value — expect 400
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/me/visibility
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "student_id": "{{studentId}}",
  "visibility": "STEALTH",
  "hidden_fields": []
}

###

