### =============================================================================
### POST /me/lock-card — Settings → danger zone
### =============================================================================

### [17] Lock card — requires confirmation string "LOCK"
POST {{baseUrl}}/me/lock-card
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "student_id": "{{studentId}}",
  "confirmation": "LOCK"
}

###

### [18] Wrong confirmation string — expect 400 VALIDATION_ERROR
POST {{baseUrl}}/me/lock-card
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "student_id": "{{studentId}}",
  "confirmation": "lock"
}

###

### =============================================================================
### POST /me/request-replace — Settings screen
### =============================================================================

### [19] Request card replacement
POST {{baseUrl}}/me/request-replace
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "student_id": "{{studentId}}",
  "reason": "Card was lost during school trip on 15 March 2026"
}

###

### =============================================================================
### DELETE /me — Settings → danger zone
### =============================================================================

### [20] Delete account (soft delete)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

